{"tid":303341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[泰運毒案］牙朗家姐指細老勤奮孝順心地善良好無辜好冤枉","createTime":"2017-06-30T06:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T04:37:36.000Z","uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"403ce9cc15f57be1c3cc5aeea5a1a9274fe353e6","tid":303341,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/135823_47cce137b7363489554e72bfdb515132.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F135823_47cce137b7363489554e72bfdb515132.jpg&h=4b593886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【本報訊】3名香港青年月初從巴西飛往泰國，入境時被揭發行李暗格內藏合共12.3公斤可卡因，面臨最高刑罰無期徒刑。其中24歲男事主邱傑朗的姊姊指，弟弟兩年前在facebook隨手加了另一被捕女子為朋友，近月女子招人帶貨，一向打散工的邱以為兼職可順道旅遊便應徵，現面臨或要在泰國囚終身。協助他們的立法會議員涂謹申促本港警方幫忙揪出幕後指使者，徹查事件。<br />\n記者：馬志剛<br />\n邱傑朗姊姊阿Ling（化名）自弟弟被捕後3次飛往泰國探望，憶述初次探望時邱傑朗沒有鞋穿，亦已餓了幾天，連水也沒有，僅靠其他囚友分發少量食物充飢。因為泰國監獄政策與港有別，要靠家人匯款才能在監獄內購買食物和用品；阿朗既不會泰文，亦不適應環境，情緒很不穩定，「每次見佢都喊得好勁，話唔想冇做錯事都要坐一世監」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/135859_8d5e824e05b993259c50da95fd8d3f74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F135859_8d5e824e05b993259c50da95fd8d3f74.jpg&h=7838ce15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿Ling說，弟弟約於兩年前在facebook的建議好友欄目，加了今次案件的其中一名女事主為朋友，但一直沒有交流，直至今年3月左右，弟弟看到該女子發佈招人訊息才聯絡應徵。<br />\n阿Ling指弟弟無經濟壓力，「如果要用錢可以問屋企人，每月一萬幾千都冇問題」，又說他一直有打散工，掛單司機、洗頭甚至地盤都做過。她指家人因不諳英語甚少出外旅遊，至近年阿Ling才和弟弟外遊日本、泰國，相信弟弟既為兼職賺錢，又為免費旅遊而誤墮運毒陷阱。<br />\n阿Ling坦言，弟弟在港確有案底，但只是打架等性質輕微罪行，亦已受法律制裁，與毒品完全無關；她稱翻查弟弟的出入境紀錄，對上一次入境泰國就是和她去旅行，故相信他所說「以為幫人拎吓嘢」，對行李內藏毒品不知情，首次「開工」便出事。她希望弟弟能得到公平審訊，現時要等到8月底才上庭，此前「要自己諗辦法證明自己冇罪」。<br />\n涂謹申表示，據報指使各人行動的港人「明姐」在事發當日已潛逃返港，涂已去信香港警方要求全力協助調查真相，並計劃下周一聯同事主家屬和泰國律師，前往泰國駐香港總領事館遞信，促泰國當局全力追查案件主謀，徹查事件。"},{"pid":"c43c0937b089bbe50c790f863ece9d3695dda4b9","tid":303341,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:05:47.000Z","msg":"家姐眼中好細老罪行一覽<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/140230_af7aac4863cf4202087b7af1d4d5dde8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F140230_af7aac4863cf4202087b7af1d4d5dde8.jpg&h=095261d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/140243_4f82ef9719153a3508f7d07e720241c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F140243_4f82ef9719153a3508f7d07e720241c5.jpg&h=2fce2893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/140258_93095076a62d0212a38e183dde76be39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F140258_93095076a62d0212a38e183dde76be39.jpg&h=5e1b46c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/140312_7e2134175386eb4fbdfc57ab49d14dc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F140312_7e2134175386eb4fbdfc57ab49d14dc2.jpg&h=35ff4076&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與十一歲小六女生性交<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongcaselaw.com/hksar-v-yau-kit-long/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongcaselaw.com%2Fhksar-v-yau-kit-long%2F&d=EfBRsQ8Y9NwBYfX3EX3kCf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=4f52c53f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongcaselaw.com/hksar-v-yau-kit-long/</a>"},{"pid":"3b0a022375a874da9767e9cf30f143b8e7d079e7","tid":303341,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:10:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08fa7eb052240167ee33bec48dec5850b8105032","tid":303341,"uid":39539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/141149_67510c4c2a9adec9fe9cb2205609fe82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F141149_67510c4c2a9adec9fe9cb2205609fe82.jpg&h=c52b10dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牙欣呢單野要一個人攬上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3853b1152b2c1b4c243412d0480d53ff7a38712e","tid":303341,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:12:33.000Z","msg":"呢班友而家出黎扮無知搏同情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12f7531673e0b804ee05cad0f20bac0881fc6a3","tid":303341,"uid":26084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:14:28.000Z","msg":"牙你老母"},{"pid":"5cd25511a3327a1bb057544da457ace7af3a77e0","tid":303341,"uid":37153,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"公平審訊咪坐成世囉"},{"pid":"14643d53dd4689a017baee7f1b6f701ce5b28eda","tid":303341,"uid":120070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"一個古惑仔 請你長期要飛都幾搞笑 <br />\n開左條新Airline 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 古惑航行?<br />\n比個空少你做呀"},{"pid":"f836cc208bb6e7563258eed8ba75c7b540ed471e","tid":303341,"uid":108311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:22:55.000Z","msg":"屋企人可以聲淚俱下保件垃圾<br />\n殊不簡單"},{"pid":"78922a62420036133b8bcb1f10a9267c4c018735","tid":303341,"uid":64680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:25:40.000Z","msg":"屌你老母斷正都話無辜"},{"pid":"17d023c71e3bfb261f50073e851646f1e71ab078","tid":303341,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:28:24.000Z","msg":"有晒前科都可以幫佢講好說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bb0fb0fb41cbf6fdead0c2f8f1cf9a14fdf3d8","tid":303341,"uid":48743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"無打你靶都要偷笑喇，想無罪釋放係咪high大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a683e65c637be1d1f640c62285424986ef74d92c","tid":303341,"uid":1139,"li